text: Lennert Impens (born 24 February 1995) is a Belgian korfball player. He is a member of and the Belgium national korfball team. Impens became a member of the national team in 2021. He won with the team the silver medal the 2021 European Korfball Championship. Pauwels became 2022 . With the national team he won the silver medal at the 2022 World Games in Birmingham, Alabama. ==Achievements== ===Club=== *Topkorfbal League champion, 1x (2022) *, 1x (2022) ===National team=== ; World Games : 2022 World Games ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian korfball players
